This company is expected to have issued several invoices for the sale of computer components in the total value of HUF about 18 million between October and December 2005.
According to the investigating authority, the Cash Investment Kft. from Kiskunhalas, which has been in liquidation since 14 September 2005, is expected to have acted as the buyer of these invoices.
