In the consumer goods manufacturing sectors, a price increase of 6.8 percent was noted, and in the fixed goods, a price reduction of 1.4 percent was noted.
Industrial export prices in Forint increased by 1.1 percent in August compared to the previous month, but fell by 3.9 percent year-on-year.
